            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Note: was able to reproduce with a commit dating before libvterm's vendoring, so this is not caused by reflow. In fact, reflow improves the situation: going from two windows to one window \"fixes\" the problem with reflow, while without it the problems subsists.",
